Elise Larnicol https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elise_Larnicol 0 Elise Larnicol is a French film, television, and theatre actress. She was a member of the troop Les Robins des Bois (The Robinhoods), a French humoristic troop formed in 1996 with Pierre-François Martin-Laval, Jean-Paul Rouve, Marina Foïs and others.
